><br />\n<br />\n諗諗下都幾浪費。可以用來做皮草"},{"pid":"f7f29879383e4f28afb7045f7ce1e781d727bc9f","tid":35143,"uid":6045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"貓奴本性就係on9<br />\n偽大愛嘅垃圾"},{"pid":"a5536df93f09721ab0b1cacc32c5ac3eb4dfa3de","tid":35143,"uid":49275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"見到你班on9我都覺好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf25c48fda45a2219f3e8a9b36afaea0dcf9cad","tid":35143,"uid":50391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到你班on9我都覺好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n互嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c62fa9670dd75313c5e9da393506e22c1b794d","tid":35143,"uid":6045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓奴本性就係on9<br />\n偽大愛嘅垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n物種共存 跟本就唔應該拎黎比你當寵物玩 <br />\n亦唔需要做任何野刻意傷害佢地"},{"pid":"620fd7e7970fbd53f1408d528cf60bca2181e270","tid":35143,"uid":6045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貓奴本性就係on9<br />\n偽大愛嘅垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n物種共存 跟本就唔應該拎黎比你當寵物玩 <br />\n亦唔需要做任何野刻意傷害佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9873cbe5dc64b571eb769697daf752b803075c21","tid":35143,"uid":12013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"貓冇問題 我都好中意<br />\n但果ｄ屌9人ge貓奴就十分之on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇養過撚知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6eb9055c190a40ad9f214e088d048c6ccf86d1","tid":35143,"uid":50391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貓奴本性就係on9<br />\n偽大愛嘅垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n物種共存 跟本就唔應該拎黎比你當寵物玩 <br />\n亦唔需要做任何野刻意傷害佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係班人上晒腦，要全世界都鐘意貓，好心餵下野貓又俾人屌無常識，痴撚晒線咁。咁咪俾佢地睇下唔鐘意貓嘅人，其實都可以好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07749fed270cfb6f3530738072c277ddf79cb801","tid":35143,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"你真係當愛協一個電話就同你搞咩傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年中都唔知有幾多你呢種柒頭想借刀殺貓， 個個打個電話就話殺人哋咪好撚唔得閒， 真係當愛協懞㗎咩比你舞， 自以為好撚醒， 其實正白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30929bdf55687d01719e201ac68baf073bb042a8","tid":35143,"uid":6045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n物種共存 跟本就唔應該拎黎比你當寵物玩 <br />\n亦唔需要做任何野刻意傷害佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係班人上晒腦，要全世界都鐘意貓，好心餵下野貓又俾人屌無常識，痴撚晒線咁。咁咪俾佢地睇下唔鐘意貓嘅人，其實都可以好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我本身對貓neutral 見到都只係直行直過<br />\n不過啲貓奴態度真係弱鳩智"},{"pid":"755aea77f63fe59ae8dc9ffba90a247c152e5b38","tid":35143,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"其實愛協做班道德撚唔願做既野<br />\n<br />\n咁多流浪貓 又有衛生問題 又無人養<br />\n<br />\n你地又有冇捐錢比愛協先？ <br />\n<br />\n我唔覺得送去愛協有問題<br />\n<br />\n有問題係班買左之後放生既人  <br />\n<br />\n咁多流浪貓狗 多得佢地唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19955614443f95dc566fa01408ae15746215457","tid":35143,"uid":28948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:06:35.000Z","msg":"仆街啦你<br />\n講埋啲咁無人性嘅說話，啲貓又無得罪你。"},{"pid":